	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Yes of course there are dwarves living on Agalla! We have lots of races here - True Agallan Giants, Half-Giants, Dwarves, Dryads, Utraeans, some Droog in the Western Swamp... and of course a lot of Goblins working the mines. And in the farthest reaches of this planet you may even still encounter the elusive Krug.
We all live in relative harmony for centuries. Well, as it is, with some races and tribes, living in harmony basically means each side minding their own business...
Sadly there are no True Agallans here currently; well, it's off-season, of course. When they come they usually camp in tents, as the rooms here are too small for them naturally. They're quite a sight, especially from our perspective!";
	}
}
